room_title: Escape room "Russian Spy Room" by Can You Escape? in Tampa
room_description: When a famous Russian photographer Alexander Petrovich passed away in 1983, his studio was left abandoned. Upon inspection, it revealed some dark secrets about his double life. The US government was notified and you are the first FBI agents to enter the space. It will take a keen eye, some physical ingenuity and quick responses for you to escape this fun-filled room.
